---
title: Chicken Pineapple Party Tacos with Bell Pepper and Fresh Radishes
description: Gather round, everybody, it’s taco time! We encourage you to make a self-serve taco bar using this recipe’s ingredients and let all of your hungry eaters fill their tortillas just the way they like. There’s no shortage of fixings to choose from: chopped chicken coated in Mexican-style spices, a sweet and succulent pineapple salsa, a pepper and onion jumble, and slices of cool and crisp radish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w12-r5-2dd96418.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w12-r5-7018a224.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chicken-pineapple-party-tacos-589a1302a28e1a25ac3fc072
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 600 kcal
  fat: 30 g
  saturated fat: 10 g
  carbohydrates: 49 g
